  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN THE DISCORD</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Go to the end of the \"line\", you have all the time you need. If you want a challenge try to make it in less than an hour and compete for the leaderboard.<br><br>One Hour And A Straight Line (OHSL) is a mix between Parkour and FPS games with a little musical twist and a relaxed vibe.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712630/extras/1aceb740a06f157f32bcf0531fd68860.poster.avif?t=1767781382\" width=616 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712630/extras/1aceb740a06f157f32bcf0531fd68860.webm?t=1767781382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712630/extras/1aceb740a06f157f32bcf0531fd68860.mp4?t=1767781382\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >On this little linear journey you will have:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Wall Riding as the main movement mechanic. You will be wall riding/climbing 95% of the time. With an unique setup allowing complete control of your movements while wall riding.<br><br></li><li>Musical Guns instead of normal guns. Shoot to the beat of melodies.<br><br></li><li>Platform building: Farm blocks with your musical guns, then place and wallride on them to avoid gaps or obstacles and maximize your speed.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712630/extras/323c80b6a216f398bdd8fa2795669c65.poster.avif?t=1767781382\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712630/extras/323c80b6a216f398bdd8fa2795669c65.webm?t=1767781382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712630/extras/323c80b6a216f398bdd8fa2795669c65.mp4?t=1767781382\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Go to the end of the \"line\", you have all the time you need. If you want a challenge try to make it in less than an hour and compete for the leaderboard.<br><br>One Hour And A Straight Line (OHSL) is a mix between Parkour and FPS games with a little musical twist and a relaxed vibe.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712630/extras/1aceb740a06f157f32bcf0531fd68860.poster.avif?t=1767781382\" width=616 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712630/extras/1aceb740a06f157f32bcf0531fd68860.webm?t=1767781382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712630/extras/1aceb740a06f157f32bcf0531fd68860.mp4?t=1767781382\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >On this little linear journey you will have:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Wall Riding as the main movement mechanic. You will be wall riding/climbing 95% of the time. With an unique setup allowing complete control of your movements while wall riding.<br><br></li><li>Musical Guns instead of normal guns. Shoot to the beat of melodies.<br><br></li><li>Platform building: Farm blocks with your musical guns, then place and wallride on them to avoid gaps or obstacles and maximize your speed.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712630/extras/323c80b6a216f398bdd8fa2795669c65.poster.avif?t=1767781382\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712630/extras/323c80b6a216f398bdd8fa2795669c65.webm?t=1767781382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712630/extras/323c80b6a2